<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>............... عبد الملك بن عبد الله بن دهيش<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>.................. ١/ ١/١٤٢٢ هـ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>